{"tid":1563333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係和理非掩護前線而唔係前線掩護和理非","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T08:54:53.000Z","uid":35136,"like":119,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"aad9535acca14686141abde38a559c731dc7ff80","tid":1563333,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"Black block就係大家有統一衣著令popo鎖定唔到特定人士嘅特定行為<br />\n點解和理非都要black block呀<br />\n係要俾前線做完嘢融入<br />\n換完裝入一群一齊走<br />\n就算popo係各個站搜都搜到好多人係冇裝<br />\n最多係抄身份證<br />\n而家點解咁多前線俾人拉就係成日都係前線斷後和理非走晒<br />\n冇晒掩護<br />\n一搜就拉<br />\n咁多嘅和理非有啲風吹草動就走晒<br />\n淨低嘅前線就好危險<br />\n希望大家冇裝嘅話係附近商場留耐啲食個飯飲糖水<br />\n與其係屋企睇live擔心不如係附近掩護佢哋<br />\n咁先叫一齊嚟一齊走"},{"pid":"296707ac5d51e233194ff0f1664011653f647668","tid":1563333,"uid":76702,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13e9ac42117ccef04ba4e15df95206d48604e721","tid":1563333,"uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"有前線話等後面走先走"},{"pid":"fab12e65ae81ec716641cdb6d9faa8a80f6ecb78","tid":1563333,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a45c1cdd7493edd0260f411e54830329